{"sn10.7:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 10.7 ","sn10.7:0.2":"1. Indakavagga ","sn10.7:0.3":"Punabbasusutta ","sn10.7:1.1":"Ekam samayam bhagava savatthiyam viharati jetavane anathapindikassa arame. ","sn10.7:1.2":"Tena kho pana samayena bhagava bhikkhu nibbanapatisamyuttaya dhammiya kathaya sandasseti samadapeti samuttejeti sampahamseti. ","sn10.7:1.3":"Te ca bhikkhu atthim katva manasi katva sabbacetasa samannaharitva ohitasota dhammam sunanti. ","sn10.7:1.4":"Atha kho punabbasumata yakkhini puttake evam tosesi: ","sn10.7:2.1":"“Tunhi uttarike hohi, ","sn10.7:2.2":"tunhi hohi punabbasu; ","sn10.7:2.3":"Yavaham buddhasetthassa, ","sn10.7:2.4":"dhammam sossami satthuno. ","sn10.7:3.1":"Nibbanam bhagava aha, ","sn10.7:3.2":"sabbaganthappamocanam; ","sn10.7:3.3":"Ativela ca me hoti, ","sn10.7:3.4":"asmim dhamme piyayana. ","sn10.7:4.1":"Piyo loke sako putto, ","sn10.7:4.2":"piyo loke sako pati; ","sn10.7:4.3":"Tato piyatara mayham, ","sn10.7:4.4":"assa dhammassa maggana. ","sn10.7:5.1":"Na hi putto pati vapi, ","sn10.7:5.2":"piyo dukkha pamocaye; ","sn10.7:5.3":"Yatha saddhammassavanam, ","sn10.7:5.4":"dukkha moceti paninam. ","sn10.7:6.1":"Loke dukkhaparetasmim, ","sn10.7:6.2":"Jaramaranasamyute; ","sn10.7:6.3":"Jaramaranamokkhaya, ","sn10.7:6.4":"Yam dhammam abhisambudham; ","sn10.7:6.5":"Tam dhammam sotumicchami, ","sn10.7:6.6":"Tunhi hohi punabbasu”ti. ","sn10.7:7.1":"“Amma na byaharissami, ","sn10.7:7.2":"tunhibhutayamuttara; ","sn10.7:7.3":"Dhammameva nisamehi, ","sn10.7:7.4":"saddhammassavanam sukham; ","sn10.7:7.5":"Saddhammassa anannaya, ","sn10.7:7.6":"amma dukkham caramase. ","sn10.7:8.1":"Esa devamanussanam, ","sn10.7:8.2":"sammulhanam pabhankaro; ","sn10.7:8.3":"Buddho antimasariro, ","sn10.7:8.4":"dhammam deseti cakkhuma”ti. ","sn10.7:9.1":"“Sadhu kho pandito nama, ","sn10.7:9.2":"putto jato uresayo; ","sn10.7:9.3":"Putto me buddhasetthassa, ","sn10.7:9.4":"dhammam suddham piyayati. ","sn10.7:10.1":"Punabbasu sukhi hohi, ","sn10.7:10.2":"ajjahamhi samuggata; ","sn10.7:10.3":"Ditthani ariyasaccani, ","sn10.7:10.4":"uttarapi sunatu me”ti. "}